name: Radishes 8x10 Print
description:
8x10 borderless archival print printed in a professional lab on Kodak Professional Supra Endura VC Digital Paper.

The print comes unmatted and unframed. Colors may look differently in person. Watermark will not appear on the final print. Print will be signed and dated on the back.

Carefully packaged and shipped free in the US via USPS First Class.
